title: Schiefer Madness: Karma Will Prevail
description:
From bidets to porn sites, we talk about pretty much everything this episode. Thankfully it's a bonus episode, so we can do what we want! And so can you, but we'd encourage you to donate to the One Fair Wage Emergency Fund by going to OFWEmergencyFund.org. With your leftover money, feel free to buy yourself a plague doctor mask.

Buy our brand new merch! https://store.dftba.com/collections/beach-too-sandy-water-too-wet
Support us on Patreon at patreon.com/beachtoosandy for a monthly livestream Q&A!
Go subscribe to our YouTube channel and watch our first ever live show in New York! www.youtube.com/c/beachtoosandywatertoowet
Logo by Courtney Aventura. Theme by Mavus White.
Music by PSOVOD and tyops.
